      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8 text-center text-gray-900">
        Drilling Challenges in Lucknow? We Have Proven Solutions
      </h2>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-red-600">
            Lucknow's Boring Problems
          </h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="font-bold text-red-600">❌</span>
              <span
                ><strong>Clay-Heavy Soil:</strong> Lucknow's black soil clogs cheap
                machines. Breakdowns mid-job.</span
              >
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="font-bold text-red-600">❌</span>
              <span
                ><strong>Distance from Support:</strong> Local dealers take 2–3 days
                for repairs. Lost income.</span
              >
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="font-bold text-red-600">❌</span>
              <span
                ><strong>Spare Parts Shortage:</strong> Hydraulic seals, pistons stuck
                for weeks. Production halts.</span
              >
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="font-bold text-red-600">❌</span>
              <span
                ><strong>High Fuel Costs:</strong> Inefficient engines burn ₹300–500/day.
                Profit margins shrink 20%.</span
              >
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-teal-50 p-8 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-teal-900">
            Our Lucknow-Optimized Solution
          </h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="font-bold text-green-600">✓</span>
              <span
                ><strong>Clay-Proven Design:</strong> 30 HP hydraulic model handles
                Lucknow's dense soil. 250–400 feet guaranteed.</span
              >
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="font-bold text-green-600">✓</span>
              <span
